title: (Thurs Full) Lunchbox’s Woodstock 69 Report + Easy Listening Country Music Game + Bobby and Eddie’s PlayStation Friend Stops By
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) Lunchbox’s Woodstock 69 Report + Easy Listening Country Music Game + Bobby and Eddie’s PlayStation Friend Stops By
description:
Bobby assigned Lunchbox with the task of preparing a report on Woodstock 69 after bringing it up during a music history segment last week. Lunchbox did his research and shared the mind-blowing report with you! Raymundo plays the “Easy Listening” version of a famous country song and Bobby, Amy, Eddie and Lunchbox have to name the song! Bobby and Eddie made a friend playing video games online. Video Game Andrew stops by the studio and shares what it was like becoming friends with Bobby while playing NBA 2k.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
